"content": "<h2>A time and place for humour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:1-Eccl3:4\">ECC 3:1–3:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Touches of humour in Scripture</h2>\n<h3>Things people found funny</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:12\">GEN 18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:17\">GEN 17:17</a></p>\n<h3>Humour at others' expense</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:4\">JOB 12:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>OT writers found wordplay humorous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:10-Mic1:11\">MIC 1:10–1:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Some passages seem to have a humorous intent</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:27\">1KI 18:27</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:24\">19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:42\">LUK 6:42</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:13-Acts12:16\">ACT 12:13–12:16</a></p>",
